story: Chief Skullface is an unknown native American who agreed to let Dr. Death change his body into a monstrous, but powerful form. The process warped his mind, turning him into a murderous creature of evil.
Chief Skullface is immune to most blunt and piercing damage, such as fists, bullets, knives, and arrows.
Chief Skullface is immortal, like all creatures from the Beyond. If his body is severely damaged or destroyed, his spirit will return to the Beyond where the body can regenerate.
